{"tid":2103253,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"未投票既 麻煩入黎望下先！","createTime":"2020-07-11T05:21:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-11T06:08:39.000Z","uid":108987,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c4290c0dc463dcf297171bed26c6ea5f14147972","tid":2103253,"uid":108987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T05:21:32.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">今日大部分人都有兩票 有地區同超區 投票果陣會問你係咪傳統功能組別（即區議會（第二）以外嘅選民 你要簡「否」先投到超區</span></span>"},{"pid":"91a4c933332273e1ae634d455d4308dd8e79fec1","tid":2103253,"uid":108987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4290c0dc463dcf297171bed26c6ea5f14147972","tid":2103253,"uid":108987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T05:21:32.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">今日大部分人都有兩票 有地區同超區 投票果陣會問你係咪傳統功能組別（即區議會（第二）以外嘅選民 你要簡「否」先投到超區</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T05:29:55.000Z","msg":"個問題有啲fake 即係如果你係區議會（第二）嘅選民 就要簡否<br />\n<br />\n如果唔記得自己係咪區議會（第二）嘅選民 仲係屋企嘅就上選舉事務處網頁查返 <span class=\"x-large\">但如果你已經係票站範圍 麻煩你<span class=\"red\">唔好</span>上選舉事務處網查 要查既就行去遠離初選票站嘅地方 或者憑你記憶去簡</span>"},{"pid":"525acc0fe79f2f87f70562ab8a921c458fd9ebae","tid":2103253,"uid":2110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T05:31:01.000Z","msg":"投票攻略：<br />\n加快投票流程步驟, 避免輪到你先黎搞造成阻礙<br />\n<br />\n1.睇自己準備去邊個地方投, 再搵返個票站編號<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1rTHp9g2UfTax1rQMgJEyQ6CEjHdJUXHw/view\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffile%2Fd%2F1rTHp9g2UfTax1rQMgJEyQ6CEjHdJUXHw%2Fview&d=FEUhZFrEoh9TukhHyG%2BZyNqeVONt7zbw7GHn8%2FjWPdo%3D&h=3cd4766e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/file/d/1rTHp9g2UfTax1rQMgJEyQ6CEjHdJUXHw/view</a><br />\n<br />\n2. 入去依度輸入票站個號碼<br />\n<a href=\"https://webapp.popvote.hk/onboarding\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwebapp.popvote.hk%2Fonboarding&d=FEUhZFrEoh9TukhHyG%2BZyNqeVONt7zbw7GHn8%2FjWPdo%3D&h=f12dd4e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://webapp.popvote.hk/onboarding</a><br />\n<br />\n3. 拎到個QR CODE之後再screen capture , save低<br />\n<br />\n4. 之後再帶住址證明+screen capture+身分證<br />\n去1.揀左嘅票站投票<br />\n<br />\n5. 投超區記得要選「否」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其他資料：<a href=\"https://landing.popvote.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flanding.popvote.hk%2F&d=FEUhZFrEoh9TukhHyG%2BZyNqeVONt7zbw7GHn8%2FjWPdo%3D&h=22269d97\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://landing.popvote.hk/</a>"},{"pid":"123aec4f6f835d69cf14ef0e149e6026990daa7b","tid":2103253,"uid":108987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T05:32:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"61b972eeac9f8680bc28c94caecfbb4b33ec0944","tid":2103253,"uid":491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T05:32:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>加快投票流程步驟, 避免輪到你先黎搞造成阻礙<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">1.睇自己準備去邊個地方投, 再搵返個票站編號</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1rTHp9g2UfTax1rQMgJEyQ6CEjHdJUXHw/view\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffile%2Fd%2F1rTHp9g2UfTax1rQMgJEyQ6CEjHdJUXHw%2Fview&d=FEUhZFrEoh9TukhHyG%2BZyNqeVONt7zbw7GHn8%2FjWPdo%3D&h=3cd4766e\" target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/file/d/1rTHp9g2UfTax1rQMgJEyQ6CEjHdJUXHw/view</a><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JX2zheN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJX2zheN.jpg&h=99f58ff2&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mghjtmt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMghjtmt.jpg&h=36cce745&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A3LMSN9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA3LMSN9.jpg&h=c5ff20af&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mXiKEs9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmXiKEs9.jpg&h=56bd1c26&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"htt